docs.text:
The server can be configured by editing the  homecage/homecage_app/config.json  file.  cd
pico homecage/homecage_app/config.json  The default file is:  {
     hardware :{
         irLightPin : 7,
         whiteLightPin : 8,
         temperatureSensor : 9
    },
     lights :{
         sunrise : 6,
         sunset : 18
    },
     video :{
         fps : 30,
         resolution : [1024,768],
         fileDuration : 6,
         captureStill : true,
         stillInterval : 2
    },
     stream : {
         streamResolution : [1024,768]
    }
}
